1. *Prate* ga već dva meseca. (They have been following him for two months.)
2. Oni su *pratili* njegov put. (They tracked his journey.)
3. *Pratila* je njegovu riječ. (She followed his word.)
4. Oni su *pratili* njegove korake. (They followed his steps.)
5. *Prateći* ga, saznali su šta radi. (By following him, they found out what he was doing.)